3-dead-first-responders-quarantined-over-toxic-exposure/articleshow/131239263.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T09:27:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131239328,imgsize-88520.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Another military operation on cards? USS Nimitz enters Caribbean amid US-Cuba tensions]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131238769.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Amidst escalating US-Cuba tensions, the USS Nimitz strike group has entered the Caribbean. This follows President Trump's intensified rhetoric and a recent indictment of former Cuban President Raul Castro. The US is increasing pressure on Havana, citing economic hardship and past incidents, though Trump downplays fears of direct military action.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/another-military-operation-on-cards-uss-nimitz-enters-caribbean-amid-us-cuba-tensions/articleshow/131238769.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/another-military-operation-on-cards-uss-nimitz-enters-caribbean-amid-us-cuba-tensions/articleshow/131238769.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T09:14:08+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131239047,imgsize-59308.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘Hair on fire’: Trump, Netanyahu call turns tense over Iran strategy]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131238256.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[US President Trump and Israeli PM Netanyahu clashed over Iran diplomacy, with Trump favoring a deal and Netanyahu pushing for military action.  Mediators from Qatar, Pakistan, and others are working on a revised proposal, but Trump warns the window for talks is closing, while Israel remains on high alert.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hair-on-fire-donald-trump-netanyahu-call-turns-tense-as-both-leaders-clash-over-iran-strategy/articleshow/131238256.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/hair-on-fire-donald-trump-netanyahu-call-turns-tense-as-both-leaders-clash-over-iran-strategy/articleshow/131238256.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T07:37:50+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131238933,imgsize-32288.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["Charlie was about to update his will": Candace Owens sparks backlash after explosive Charlie Kirk conspiracy claims on livestream]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131237650.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens sparked major backlash after a controversial livestream filled with conspiracy claims surrounding Charlie Kirk, criticism of Victor Marx, and comments about Joe Rogan and Theo Von. Owens claimed “something isn’t adding up” regarding Kirk’s death and suggested hidden motives tied to his will and communications. Critics on X accused her of pushing conspiracies without evidence, calling the broadcast chaotic and misleading.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlie-was-about-to-update-his-will-candace-owens-sparks-backlash-after-explosive-charlie-kirk-conspiracy-claims-on-livestream/articleshow/131237650.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/charlie-was-about-to-update-his-will-candace-owens-sparks-backlash-after-explosive-charlie-kirk-conspiracy-claims-on-livestream/articleshow/131237650.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T05:20:47+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131237650,imgsize-42026.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Was Nina Lin arrested? Twitch streamer claims missed $4 scissors scan led to night in jail]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131237590.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Nina Lin revealed on Twitch that she allegedly spent a night in jail after failing to scan a $4 pair of scissors during self checkout. The streamer claimed it was an honest mistake caused by rushing through checkout, but store staff still involved police. The incident reignited debate online because Nina previously faced similar shoplifting accusations in 2025. She also suggested critics linked to Adin Ross and Asmongold may have influenced the situation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/was-nina-lin-arrested-twitch-streamer-claims-missed-4-scissors-scan-led-to-night-in-jail/articleshow/131237590.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/was-nina-lin-arrested-twitch-streamer-claims-missed-4-scissors-scan-led-to-night-in-jail/articleshow/131237590.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T04:32:43+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131237590,imgsize-55498.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Tennessee man jailed for 37 days over Charlie Kirk meme to receive $835,000 settlement]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131235387.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA