retary David Lammy unveiled plans to cut youth custody by 25%, inspired by his own experiences growing up in Tottenham. The reforms aim to reduce pre-trial detentions, introduce youth intervention courts, and enhance parental accountability.  These measures seek to divert children from crime and prevent future offending by offering community sentences and specialized support.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/david-lammy-unveils-reforms-to-reduce-youth-jail-terms-and-protect-vulnerable-children-in-the-uk/articleshow/131230849.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/david-lammy-unveils-reforms-to-reduce-youth-jail-terms-and-protect-vulnerable-children-in-the-uk/articleshow/131230849.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-20T21:46:56+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131230867,imgsize-15990.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Indian realtor in NZ says neighbour urinated on fence: 'My family and I have...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131228838.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-realtor-in-new-zealand-says-neighbour-urinated-on-fence-egged-cars-my-family-and-i-have-/articleshow/131228838.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/indian-realtor-in-new-zealand-says-neighbour-urinated-on-fence-egged-cars-my-family-and-i-have-/articleshow/131228838.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-20T21:31:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131230635,imgsize-89732.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[World Bee Day campaign encourages public to protect declining UK pollinators]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131230508.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The RSPCA urges public support for declining bee populations, with a third lost in three decades, impacting vital crops. Initiatives like the South Downs' Bee Lines project create wildflower habitats. Experts highlight bees' intelligence and complex lives, emphasizing simple actions like providing water and planting native flowers can significantly aid their survival and welfare.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/world-bee-day-campaign-encourages-public-to-protect-declining-uk-pollinators/articleshow/131230508.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/world-bee-day-campaign-encourages-public-to-protect-declining-uk-pollinators/articleshow/131230508.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-20T21:20:38+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131230520,imgsize-37528.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scotland: Jenny Gilruth expected to become Deputy First Minister in new SNP team]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131230293.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Scotland's First Minister John Swinney is set to announce his new cabinet. Jenny Gilruth is tipped to become Deputy First Minister. Swinney was sworn in for his second term. His government will focus on the cost-of-living crisis and NHS reforms. The SNP won 58 seats in the recent election. New appointments are expected soon.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/scotland-jenny-gilruth-expected-to-become-deputy-first-minister-in-new-snp-team/articleshow/